2. Natural Earth 1:110m Admin-0 Countries (vector basemap outline)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
   FireWatch's offline vector basemap (ADR-0052) ships a world-outline derived
   from Natural Earth data. Natural Earth is released into the public domain and
   carries no attribution requirement; it is credited here as a courtesy.

